# TQ-1: Test Coverage Requirement
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Every feature and bug fix

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Test Coverage: Degree to which code is exercised by tests.

ENFORCE: All new or changed functionality must have automated tests before merge.
PROHIBIT: Missing or incomplete tests; merging without coverage confirmation.
ON VIOLATION: Halt skill execution → notify orchestrator and engineer.
